{"tid":1362063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解成個熱門冇一個post係講7.28","createTime":"2019-07-24T18:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:47:41.000Z","uid":205248,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"f592bca9a6a64e1fbfb764f092fe131fbd952e3a","tid":1362063,"uid":205248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:19:56.000Z","msg":"我明白7.27元朗嘅行動係重要 但依家個焦點去哂元朗到 好少人提到7.21黑警冇預警開6槍 總共開咗36槍<br />\n有巴打比黑警瞄準個頭嚟射 有記者比黑警用催淚彈打到隻手瘀咗<br />\n小弟懇求大家喺元朗個邊分返少少注意力落7.28個遊行到 唔要求大家全神貫注落7.28個遊行到<br />\n但起碼要知到個日喺遮打花園有遊行<br />\n依家完全係冇乜人提上環開槍<br />\n亦有義士被捕<br />\n<br />\n小弟喺呢到求下大家都多啲推下7.28嘅post<br />\n同埋集中返<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 撤回逃犯修訂引渡條例<br />\n2. 撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放被捕義士<br />\n4.成立獨立調查委員會 還警察清白<br />\n5. 立即以行政命令解散立法會 實行真雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wc6JAVo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWc6JAVo.png&h=6fd45ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tHwKOK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tHwKOK.png&h=38119812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7.28只有一個追究開槍大遊行<br />\n其他地區遊行已經改期<br />\n<br />\n727 元朗反黑<br />\n728 中上環追究開槍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"fb0a9b8cdf70cab1b1343518eebeb3c26edf51a7","tid":1362063,"uid":205248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:21:48.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"2d0e1c04df73db910842b9176ed0b2ed2c9afd86","tid":1362063,"uid":205248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:22:18.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"710c1d0c8639764c8876df0d7a47ec44ce599669","tid":1362063,"uid":205248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:22:30.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"ee49621893